               <p>I live at <placeName id="t17890603-54-crimeloc266">the Coach and Horses at Hampstead</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17890603-54-crimeloc266" type="placeName" value="the Coach and Horses at Hampstead"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17890603-54-crimeloc266" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890603-54-off264 t17890603-54-crimeloc266"></join>; on the 25th of last month I lost a linen shirt, and a yard of muslin; they were taken out of my box, near my bed-side, I am a servant at the house; I suspected the prisoner, the shirt and muslin were both together, he slept in the same room, he came away from his master's that night; I have seen him at his master's.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17890603-54-person538">
                  ROBERT
                   BLAKE
