                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I lost a hat the same time, I slept in the same room; there were two beds, I never got my hat; when he was taken he owned he had left it at one place and another, but we could not find it; I never saw him before, I said nothing to him.</p>
               <p>
            
